Gem Diamonds Posts Record $28.9 Million First-Half Profit as Prices Soar

-- B y   J o h n   V i l j o e n
-- 
2011-08-19T06:05:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-19/gem-diamonds-posts-record-28-9-million-first-half-profit-as-prices-soar.html
Gem Diamonds Ltd. (GEMD) , a producer of the
stones in Southern Africa, said first-half attributable profit
was a record $28.9 million, or 20.89 cents a share, after rough
diamond prices reached all-time highs. Gem Diamonds commented in
a statement in  London  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  